            <abstract>
                <p>A miniature illustrating <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3615Miracle"/> typically 
                    with as a sequence of six episodes/events, showing: first, the cannibal surrounded by the bodies of those he killed; second, the peasant and other inhabitants fleeing from
                the cannibal, with several houses depicted in the background; third, the cannibal offering water to a beggar covered by sores of leprosy; fourth, the demons holding the
                cannibal's soul among the flames of hell before <persName ref="PRS5684JesusCh"/> sitting on a throne; fifth, <persName ref="PRS6819Mary"/>, who holds the soul of the cannibal,
                    standing before
                    <persName ref="PRS5684JesusCh"/> and sixth; two <term key="angel">angels</term> weighing the cannibal's good and bad deeds in a scale.</p>
            </abstract>
